{"tid":1424284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問一下 最近D黑警係咪唔洗做?","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T15:50:12.000Z","uid":150921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"11d9c7bb9dfdb8cc7c15a2d8460432f3be1a2aba","tid":1424284,"uid":150921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:37:37.000Z","msg":"D狗係咪日日坐係個環頭涼冷氣等出動<br />\n出親車閒閒地都十架 幾十至一百隻狗咁爬出黎<br />\n唔撚洗做? 唔撚洗捉賊反黑?<br />\n哦~原來納稅人出錢就係比D狗鳩坐涼冷氣<br />\n等D納稅人 仲日日掛住返工交稅 驚死D狗無狗糧食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要袋8萬一個月 見撚住你班港奴返工真係笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁中意養狗點解唔養隻聽話識hand hand既<br />\n反而中意養隻得閒咬鳩主人既狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇D好中意返工既人出黎解釋下?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc86a0bd0788c8a9c253884adbee39333c3b92c","tid":1424284,"uid":150921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/26ef0002dc3b39eb2dfb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2F26ef0002dc3b39eb2dfb&h=c3755146&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70bfba5e234f1c6f0af4caf61269128a52b456a4","tid":1424284,"uid":150921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d5021379697d7d784777f8f81a76c57c790170","tid":1424284,"uid":150921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}